without it Windows HS Activator 1.0 would not have been possible.

This activator will activate your Windows Home Server forever.

It also allows Microsoft Updates.

To confirm whether your Windows Home Server is activated, run the following command 

at the run dialog or command prompt "%systemRoot%system32oobemsoobe.exe /A" 

without the quotes.

It should show "Windows is already activated."

This Windows Home Server Activator Version 1.0 also works on Windows Home Server PowerPack 1 

and Windows Home Server PowerPack 2.
